<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
    <!-- ZMDI Material Design Iconic Font CDN -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/material-design-iconic-font@2.2.0/dist/css/material-design-iconic-font.min.css"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css" />
    <title>About Us - URL Shortener</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/header.ejs') %>

    <div class="main">
      <section class="section-about">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="shortener-content">
            <!-- user login status -->
            <div class="user-status">
              <% if(user) { %>
              <div class="status-badge success">
                <i class="zmdi zmdi-check-circle"></i>
                <span>You are logged in</span>
              </div>
              <% } else { %>
              <div class="status-badge warning">
                <i class="zmdi zmdi-alert-circle"></i>
                <span>You are not logged in</span>
              </div>
              <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="shortener-form">
              <h1 class="form-title">About Our URL Shortener</h1>

              <div class="about-content">
                <p>
                  Welcome to our <strong>URL Shortener</strong> project! 🚀  
                  This platform allows you to convert long, messy URLs into short and easy-to-share links in seconds.
                </p>

                <h2>✨ Key Features</h2>
                <ul>
                  <li><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i> Shorten long URLs instantly</li>
                  <li><i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i> Secure and reliable link generation</li>
                  <li><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> Track and manage your shortened links</li>
                  <li><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i> User-friendly interface</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>🎯 Why We Built This</h2>
                <p>
                  Sharing long URLs can be inconvenient and unattractive. Our goal was to build a 
                  simple yet powerful tool that helps individuals and businesses create professional 
                  links, improve readability, and make sharing content effortless.
                </p>

                <h2>👨‍💻 Tech Stack</h2>
                <p>
                  This project is developed using <strong>Node.js, Express, MySQL</strong>, and 
                  <strong>EJS</strong> templates. For styling, we use modern CSS and responsive 
                  layouts to ensure a clean and smooth user experience.
                </p>

                <h2>📬 Get in Touch</h2>
                <p>
                  Have questions or feedback? Visit our <a href="/contact">Contact Page</a> and drop us a message.  
                  We’d love to hear from you!
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %>
  </body>
</html>
